A dramatic cyberpunk cityscape at night where massive glowing server towers rise like skyscrapers, connected by neon-blue data streams flowing between them. In the foreground, a lone figure in a long coat stands on a rooftop, looking down at a floating platform holding packed cargo containers and shipping crates that are lifting off into the dark sky toward a distant, alternative city of servers on the horizon. The containers trail streams of luminous data particles behind them like comet tails. The scene conveys movement, transition, and strategic escape, with rain-slicked surfaces reflecting the magenta and cyan lights of the technological metropolis. Dark storm clouds gather overhead, pierced by shafts of light from the departing data vessels.
